Good firewall tool ... Iptables

Replacement ... nftables

How Iptables Works 
------------------
Comparing network traffic ... against a set of rules 

Criteria used ... packet protocol type, source or destination address or port

Target ... when dfined pattern matches, action taken

Rules are organized into ... Chains
A packet is checked sequentially

Three(3) Default Chains 
INPUT : handles packets TO server

OUTPUT : handles packets FROM server

FORWARD : handles packets destined for other servers 
